data.description: Charming carriage home in Colonial Heritage has 2,180 sqft with 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Delightful Belvedere floor plan. The 2 story Great Room has a vaulted ceiling, crown molding, carpet and ceiling fan. The Dining Room has LVP flooring. Cozy Kitchen features gas cooking, recessed lighting, stainless appliances, tile flooring and breakfast bar. Darling Sunroom has LVP flooring and sliding door access to the stone patio. The first-floor laundry room has access to the garage. 1st floor Primary bedroom has an en-suite bath with walk-in shower, walk-in closet and carpet. Upstairs is a loft area with LVP floors and ceiling fan. There are 2 other nice size bedrooms, both with skylights and ceiling fans. Finished storage in the walk-in attic. 1 Car attached garage. Enjoy all the amenities in this gated active adult 55+ community.
